snippet.title: Geoff Gets Possessed | We Are Not Alone Indie Game Devlog #24
snippet.description:
I recorded this while my face was half numb from the dentist. Also I'm hoping I didn't call Geoff the wrong name *again*.

► Checkout the Indiegogo campaign: https://igg.me/at/wearenotalone/

► Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2249440/We_Are_Not_Alone/
